learning_outcomes.en:
After having successfully passed the course a student:
- applies appropriate methods in order to secure reliability and security of communication networks;
- utilises wired and wireless Ethernet solutions and protocols;
- interconnect terminals and network nodes as well as different nodes in a network, explains the operation of the communication system created;
- selects mobile access technologies and evaluates factors that have impact on connection quality;
- monitors different data streams on different layers of the networks (incl. sound, images, video).

grade_evaluation.et:
Lõpphinne õppeaine eest koosneb järgmistest 3. põhiosadest (maks. 100 punkti):
1) Praktilised ülesanned (8x5pt);
2) Koduülesanne (1x10pt);
3) Eksam: E-test (40pt) + praktiline töö (10pt)
